Blastoise (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0008: Wartortle
Pokémon
#0010: Caterpie →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Blastoise (TCG Pocket).

Blastoise has been featured on 26 different cards since it debuted in the Base Set of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Blastoise cards are normally Water-type Stage 2 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Blastoise

Blastoise
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
